public enum EventCaching
extends Enum<EventCaching>

EventCaching options for OpRaiseEvent. This is an enum because it contains all possible options and is non-extensible.

Enum Constant Summary
DoNotCache
          Default value (not sent).
MergeCache
          Will merge this event's keys with those already cached.
RemoveCache
          Removes this event (by eventCode) from the cache.
ReplaceCache
          Replaces the event cache for this eventCode with this event's content.
